cs.DB, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.PL, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the ANSI SQL-92 standard for database management systems, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses isolation levels, which are related to concurrency control (cs.DC) and distributed systems (cs.DS). The paper proposes new phenomena to better characterize isolation types, which could fall under programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE).
